WEBVTT

00:01.754 --> 00:04.790
<i>It's an acute acceleration</i>
<i>of the disease,</i>

00:04.824 --> 00:07.093
<i>muscle rigidity,</i>
<i>whole body tremors.</i>

00:07.127 --> 00:08.260
It's progressing.

00:08.294 --> 00:09.728
- <i>I saw Emma.</i>
- <i>How is she?</i>

00:09.762 --> 00:10.729
<i>Angry.</i>

00:10.763 --> 00:11.763
It's called Lewy Body.

00:11.797 --> 00:13.932
<i>He has</i>
<i>three to five years.</i>

00:13.966 --> 00:14.933
You need
to do something!

00:14.967 --> 00:15.934
Don't you fucking dare

00:15.968 --> 00:17.436
to judge my actions.

00:17.470 --> 00:18.737
If you don't get her out,
I swear...

00:18.771 --> 00:20.139
You'll do what?

00:20.173 --> 00:22.575
Well she's getting traction
with this anti-felon thing.

00:22.609 --> 00:24.877
Apparently she's raised
over 3 million this quarter.

00:24.912 --> 00:26.145
<i>So I'm sure</i>
<i>you've seen the polls.</i>

00:26.179 --> 00:27.847
This race is a lot tighter
than anyone expected.

00:27.881 --> 00:29.982
And old Kane's MIA
in his support.

00:30.017 --> 00:32.485
This is my advice
to you.

00:32.519 --> 00:33.619
<i>Eat shit.</i>

00:33.654 --> 00:34.854
<i>( Cell phone vibrates )</i>

00:34.888 --> 00:37.656
<i>Hey, it's me.</i>
<i>I need you. Call me.</i>

00:37.691 --> 00:39.324
<i>Why'd you come home,</i>
<i>Kitty?</i>

00:39.359 --> 00:41.293
You said I could
go after Kane at will.

00:41.327 --> 00:42.894
This isn't about the Mayor.

00:42.929 --> 00:44.329
The vote is scheduled
for tomorrow.

00:44.363 --> 00:46.064
- Which?
- <i>Lennox Gardens.</i>

00:46.098 --> 00:47.798
This isn't one
we can lose.

00:47.833 --> 00:49.700
<i>I'm sure you're</i> <i>feeling the
loss</i> <i>of both Ezra and Kitty,</i>

00:49.734 --> 00:51.234
<i>but you can't do it alone.</i>

00:51.269 --> 00:53.737
Mona Fredricks has locked in the
majority of the black caucus.

00:53.771 --> 00:55.171
We could postpone the vote,

00:55.206 --> 00:56.539
give ourselves
enough time to make sure--

00:56.574 --> 00:58.641
What part of I don't want
to postpone the fucking vote

00:58.676 --> 01:00.143
do you not understand?

01:00.177 --> 01:01.378
Alderman Ross.

01:01.412 --> 01:02.412
Mona Fredricks.

01:02.446 --> 01:03.513
<i>I vote nay.</i>

01:03.547 --> 01:05.313
This is bullshit,
son of a bitch!

01:05.349 --> 01:06.482
( Shouting )

01:06.516 --> 01:08.050
The vote is suspended!

01:08.084 --> 01:09.952
Ladies and gentlemen,
Tom Kane.

01:09.986 --> 01:13.988
This airport expansion
was necessary 22 years ago.

01:14.023 --> 01:15.022
Thank you and God bless you.

01:16.858 --> 01:18.225
<i>( Gunshot )</i>

01:19.227 --> 01:20.628
Get me an ambulance now!

